{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":36,"dialogues":[],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_yi_feng","name":"伊风","alias":["吕南人"],"identity":"武林人士，本名吕南人，被萧无所害改名换姓","faction":null,"role":"protagonist","archetype":"warrior","rank":"略有小成","one_line":"本名吕南人，因被萧无所害而改名伊风，背负夺妻杀友之恨","personality":{"traits":["隐忍","坚毅","深情","果断","重义"],"speech_style":"沉稳","temperament":"内敛刚毅"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiao_nan_ping","type":"恋人","intensity":90,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"深爱"}],"known_skills":["skill_tian_xing_mi_ji"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[13],"source_refs":[{"chapter":13,"line_start":1,"line_end":8,"text":"黑暗。全然的黑暗。黑暗中，伊风能够看到的，只是脑海中出现萧南苹的那双明眸。"}]},{"id":"char_xiao_nan_ping","name":"萧南苹","alias":[],"identity":"伊风/吕南人所爱之人","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"healer","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"伊风心中所爱之人，满含爱意幽怨凄苦的明眸","personality":{"traits":["深情","温柔","执着","善良","痴情"],"speech_style":"柔声","temperament":"温柔执着"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_yi_feng","type":"恋人","intensity":90,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"深爱"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[13],"source_refs":[{"chapter":13,"line_start":4,"line_end":6,"text":"黑暗中，伊风能够看到的，只是脑海中出现萧南苹的那双明眸。那双脉脉含情的明眸。"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":2,"line_start":37,"line_end":92,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_sun_min","speaker_name":"孙敏","listener":null,"text":"谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":13,"line_start":40,"line_end":40},{"speaker":"char_yi_feng","speaker_name":"伊风","listener":"char_sun_min","text":"我，吕南人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":42,"line_end":42},{"speaker":"char_ling_lin","speaker_name":"凌琳","listener":"char_yi_feng","text":"是你？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":13,"line_start":44,"line_end":44},{"speaker":"char_yi_feng","speaker_name":"伊风","listener":"char_ling_lin","text":"不错，正是我。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":46,"line_end":46},{"speaker":"char_ling_lin","speaker_name":"凌琳","listener":"char_yi_feng","text":"你怎么会到这里来？","tone":"疑问","chapter":13,"line_start":48,"line_end":48},{"speaker":"char_yi_feng","speaker_name":"伊风","listener":"char_ling_lin","text":"不是我要来的，是人家要我来的。","tone":"无奈","chapter":13,"line_start":50,"line_end":50},{"speaker":"char_ling_lin","speaker_name":"凌琳","listener":"char_yi_feng","text":"谁要你来？","tone":"疑问","chapter":13,"line_start":52,"line_end":52},{"speaker":"char_yi_feng","speaker_name":"伊风","listener":"char_ling_lin","text":"万天萍。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":54,"line_end":54},{"speaker":"char_ling_lin","speaker_name":"凌琳","listener":"char_yi_feng","text":"他要你来干什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":13,"line_start":56,"line_end":56},{"speaker":"char_yi_feng","speaker_name":"伊风","listener":"char_ling_lin","text":"他要把我关在这里。","tone":"无奈","chapter":13,"line_start":58,"line_end":58},{"speaker":"char_ling_lin","speaker_name":"凌琳","listener":"char_yi_feng","text":"他把你关在这里？那我们岂不……","tone":"惊讶","chapter":13,"line_start":60,"line_end":60},{"speaker":"char_yi_feng","speaker_name":"伊风","listener":"char_ling_lin","text":"不错，你们也正好被关在这里。","tone":"无奈","chapter":13,"line_start":62,"line_end":62},{"speaker":"char_ling_lin","speaker_name":"凌琳","listener":"char_sun_min","text":"妈，我们出不去了。","tone":"慌张","chapter":13,"line_start":64,"line_end":64},{"speaker":"char_sun_min","speaker_name":"孙敏","listener":"char_ling_lin","text":"先别急，先问问吕少侠事情的始末再说。","tone":"平静","chapter":13,"line_start":66,"line_end":66},{"speaker":"char_sun_min","speaker_name":"孙敏","listener":"char_yi_feng","text":"这么说来，一个月后，万天萍就会救你出去？","tone":"疑问","chapter":13,"line_start":68,"line_end":69},{"speaker":"char_yi_feng","speaker_name":"伊风","listener":"char_sun_min","text":"是的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":72,"line_end":72},{"speaker":"char_sun_min","speaker_name":"孙敏","listener":"char_yi_feng","text":"我这里的粮食，够我们三个人吃半个月。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":74,"line_end":74},{"speaker":"char_ling_lin","speaker_name":"凌琳","listener":null,"text":"那半个月后？","tone":"焦急","chapter":13,"line_start":76,"line_end":76},{"speaker":"char_yi_feng","speaker_name":"伊风","listener":"char_sun_min","text":"这是你们的粮食，你们两个人吃，可以维持一个月。我反正早晚也要被万天萍杀害的……","tone":"无奈","chapter":13,"line_start":78,"line_end":80},{"speaker":"char_sun_min","speaker_name":"孙敏","listener":"char_yi_feng","text":"吕少侠别这样说，别说我们母女的性命，还是吕少侠救回来的，就算是毫不相干的人，我们也不能眼看他坐以待毙的。何况……","tone":"认真","chapter":13,"line_start":82,"line_end":84},{"speaker":"char_ling_lin","speaker_name":"凌琳","listener":"char_sun_min","text":"何况什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":13,"line_start":86,"line_end":86},{"speaker":"char_sun_min","speaker_name":"孙敏","listener":"char_ling_lin","text":"何况，也许这山洞还有别的出口。","tone":"欣慰","chapter":13,"line_start":88,"line_end":88}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_sun_min","name":"孙敏","alias":["凌夫人"],"identity":"凌琳之母","faction":null,"role":"companion","archetype":"healer","rank":"初窥门径","one_line":"凌琳之母，与女儿一同在洞窟中练功，性格稳重慈爱","personality":{"traits":["稳重","慈爱","坚韧","沉着","体贴"],"speech_style":"温和","temperament":"沉稳慈爱"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_ling_lin","type":"亲属","intensity":95,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"母女"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[13],"source_refs":[{"chapter":13,"line_start":34,"line_end":35,"text":"年纪大的赫然就是凌夫人孙敏，年纪小的就是凌琳。"}]},{"id":"char_ling_lin","name":"凌琳","alias":[],"identity":"孙敏之女，三心神君之徒","faction":null,"role":"companion","archetype":"warrior","rank":"初窥门径","one_line":"孙敏之女，三心神君弟子，性格活泼急躁","personality":{"traits":["活泼","天真","勇敢","急躁","善良"],"speech_style":"直率","temperament":"活泼急躁"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_sun_min","type":"亲属","intensity":95,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"母女"},{"target":"char_san_xin_shen_jun","type":"师徒","intensity":70,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"师徒"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[13],"source_refs":[{"chapter":13,"line_start":34,"line_end":35,"text":"年纪大的赫然就是凌夫人孙敏，年纪小的就是凌琳。"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":93,"line_end":145,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_yi_feng","speaker_name":"伊风","listener":null,"text":"没有希望了。","tone":"无奈","chapter":13,"line_start":94,"line_end":94},{"speaker":"char_ling_lin","speaker_name":"凌琳","listener":"char_yi_feng","text":"还有一个希望，也许师父会来找我们。","tone":"欣慰","chapter":13,"line_start":96,"line_end":96},{"speaker":"char_sun_min","speaker_name":"孙敏","listener":null,"text":"会吗？","tone":"疑问","chapter":13,"line_start":98,"line_end":98},{"speaker":"char_yi_feng","speaker_name":"伊风","listener":"char_ling_lin","text":"你师父是谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":13,"line_start":100,"line_end":100},{"speaker":"char_ling_lin","speaker_name":"凌琳","listener":"char_yi_feng","text":"三心神君呀。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":102,"line_end":102},{"speaker":"char_yi_feng","speaker_name":"伊风","listener":"char_ling_lin","text":"他老人家收了你做徒弟？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":13,"line_start":104,"line_end":104},{"speaker":"char_ling_lin","speaker_name":"凌琳","listener":"char_yi_feng","text":"对呀，你离开以后……","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":106,"line_end":106},{"speaker":"char_ling_lin","speaker_name":"凌琳","listener":"char_yi_feng","text":"后来师父发现这个地方．就把我们留在这里，传给我一些口诀，就离开了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":110,"line_end":112},{"speaker":"char_yi_feng","speaker_name":"伊风","listener":"char_ling_lin","text":"你们一直都在这里？","tone":"疑问","chapter":13,"line_start":114,"line_end":114},{"speaker":"char_ling_lin","speaker_name":"凌琳","listener":"char_yi_feng","text":"晤，除了昨天下午，我们下山买干粮去，到今天早上才回来。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":116,"line_end":118},{"speaker":"char_yi_feng","speaker_name":"伊风","listener":null,"text":"外面的声音，这里一点也听不到？","tone":"疑问","chapter":13,"line_start":120,"line_end":120},{"speaker":"char_sun_min","speaker_name":"孙敏","listener":"char_yi_feng","text":"我们只想清清静静地练功，所以才住到这山洞最里面，别说外头打架，就算外头山崩都听不到。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":122,"line_end":124},{"speaker":"char_ling_lin","speaker_name":"凌琳","listener":"char_yi_feng","text":"我们只想把功夫练成，去找那天争教报仇。","tone":"认真","chapter":13,"line_start":126,"line_end":126},{"speaker":"char_yi_feng","speaker_name":"伊风","listener":null,"text":"可是现在……","tone":"无奈","chapter":13,"line_start":128,"line_end":128},{"speaker":"char_sun_min","speaker_name":"孙敏","listener":"char_yi_feng","text":"吉人自有天相，我们还是安安静静地练功，急也没有用。","tone":"平静","chapter":13,"line_start":130,"line_end":132}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_san_xin_shen_jun","name":"三心神君","alias":[],"identity":"武林前辈，凌琳之师","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"monk","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"凌琳之师，传授气功剑术，发现洞窟并安置凌琳母女","personality":{"traits":["神秘","慈祥","高深莫测","爱护弟子","隐世"],"speech_style":"淡然","temperament":"神秘慈祥"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_ling_lin","type":"师徒","intensity":70,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"师徒"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[13],"source_refs":[{"chapter":13,"line_start":102,"line_end":102,"text":"凌琳道：\"三心神君呀。\""}]}],"skills":[{"id":"skill_tian_xing_mi_ji","name":"天星秘笈","type":"内功","faction":null,"rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"伊风独自钻研的内功心法秘笈","techniques":[{"id":"tech_tian_xing_nei_gong","name":"天星内功","type":"buff","description":"天星秘笈所载之内功心法，可修炼内力"}],"progression":[],"effects":[{"type":"增益","description":"修炼内功提升内力"}],"combat_style":"内力修炼","rag_refs":[13],"source_refs":[{"chapter":13,"line_start":142,"line_end":142,"text":"伊风独自钻研\"天星秘笈\"内的内功心法。"}]}],"techniques":[{"id":"tech_tian_xing_nei_gong","name":"天星内功","type":"buff","description":"天星秘笈所载之内功心法，可修炼内力","source_skill":"skill_tian_xing_mi_ji","source_refs":[{"chapter":13,"line_start":142,"line_end":142,"text":"伊风独自钻研\"天星秘笈\"内的内功心法。"}]}],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":4,"line_start":146,"line_end":213,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_wan_tian_ping","speaker_name":"万天萍","listener":"char_yi_feng","text":"想不到你果然在洞内。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":158,"line_end":158},{"speaker":"char_yi_feng","speaker_name":"伊风","listener":"char_wan_tian_ping","text":"我会不在洞内吗？","tone":"疑问","chapter":13,"line_start":160,"line_end":160},{"speaker":"char_wan_tian_ping","speaker_name":"万天萍","listener":"char_yi_feng","text":"唉！看来真的是另有其人。","tone":"无奈","chapter":13,"line_start":162,"line_end":162},{"speaker":"char_yi_feng","speaker_name":"伊风","listener":"char_wan_tian_ping","text":"另有其人？有什么人？","tone":"疑问","chapter":13,"line_start":164,"line_end":164},{"speaker":"char_wan_tian_ping","speaker_name":"万天萍","listener":"char_yi_feng","text":"老丈以为是你逃出洞外，却不意真的是另有其人，一个和你以前的相貌完全相同的人。","tone":"沉声","chapter":13,"line_start":168,"line_end":170},{"speaker":"char_yi_feng","speaker_name":"伊风","listener":"char_wan_tian_ping","text":"天争教主萧无？","tone":"疑问","chapter":13,"line_start":172,"line_end":172},{"speaker":"char_wan_tian_ping","speaker_name":"万天萍","listener":"char_yi_feng","text":"你早就知道？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":13,"line_start":174,"line_end":174},{"speaker":"char_yi_feng","speaker_name":"伊风","listener":"char_wan_tian_ping","text":"我不是说过，救你的人不是我吗？","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":176,"line_end":176},{"speaker":"char_wan_tian_ping","speaker_name":"万天萍","listener":"char_yi_feng","text":"你带的面具，怎么会和那萧无一模一样？","tone":"疑问","chapter":13,"line_start":178,"line_end":178},{"speaker":"char_yi_feng","speaker_name":"伊风","listener":"char_wan_tian_ping","text":"这我也不知道，怎么会那么巧。","tone":"无奈","chapter":13,"line_start":180,"line_end":180},{"speaker":"char_wan_tian_ping","speaker_name":"万天萍","listener":"char_yi_feng","text":"老夫的妻女婢仆，全已遭那萧无毒手。","tone":"悲痛","chapter":13,"line_start":182,"line_end":183},{"speaker":"char_wan_tian_ping","speaker_name":"万天萍","listener":"char_yi_feng","text":"这是老夫精研一生的一招剑法'飘香剑雨'，你好好钻研，日后替老夫杀了那恶贼，替老夫报仇。","tone":"恳求","chapter":13,"line_start":184,"line_end":186},{"speaker":"char_yi_feng","speaker_name":"伊风","listener":"char_wan_tian_ping","text":"万老前辈……","tone":"恳求","chapter":13,"line_start":188,"line_end":188},{"speaker":"char_wan_tian_ping","speaker_name":"万天萍","listener":"char_yi_feng","text":"你别插嘴。老夫刚才运用真气移开大石，因此体内的毒性已向上涌。老夫放你出来，目的就是要你替我复仇。从今以后。你我恩怨，一笔勾销，你可愿意？","tone":"沉声","chapter":13,"line_start":190,"line_end":194},{"speaker":"char_yi_feng","speaker_name":"伊风","listener":"char_wan_tian_ping","text":"晚辈本名吕南人，之所以改名换姓，也是那萧无所害，晚辈妻离家散，也是那萧无所赐，晚辈和他势不两立，恨不得将他生吞活剥，前辈大可放心。晚辈以吕南人三个字向前辈保证，一定手诛天争教主，除此恶贼。","tone":"豪迈","chapter":13,"line_start":198,"line_end":202},{"speaker":"char_yi_feng","speaker_name":"伊风","listener":"char_wan_tian_ping","text":"前辈！","tone":"悲痛","chapter":13,"line_start":206,"line_end":206}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_wan_tian_ping","name":"万天萍","alias":["铁面孤行客"],"identity":"武林怪杰，精研飘香剑雨剑法","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"铁面孤行客，精研飘香剑雨剑法，妻女被萧无毒害后托付遗志于吕南人","personality":{"traits":["孤傲","刚烈","重诺","坚韧","悲壮"],"speech_style":"沉声","temperament":"孤傲刚烈"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiao_wu","type":"宿敌","intensity":95,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"血仇"},{"target":"char_yi_feng","type":"合作者","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"托付遗志"}],"known_skills":["skill_piao_xiang_jian_yu"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[13],"source_refs":[{"chapter":13,"line_start":210,"line_end":210,"text":"伊风怔怔注视着\"铁面孤行客\"万天萍的尸首"}]},{"id":"char_xiao_wu","name":"萧无","alias":["天争教主"],"identity":"天争教主，与吕南人面貌相同","faction":"faction_tian_zheng_jiao","role":"villain","archetype":"assassin","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"天争教主，面貌与吕南人相同，杀害万天萍妻女婢仆，吕南人的宿敌","personality":{"traits":["阴险","残忍","狡诈","狠毒","野心勃勃"],"speech_style":"阴冷","temperament":"阴险残忍"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_yi_feng","type":"宿敌","intensity":95,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"夺妻杀友之恨"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[13],"source_refs":[{"chapter":13,"line_start":172,"line_end":173,"text":"伊风道：\"天争教主萧无？\